{"tid":2248433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港地黃圈兩大熱狗","createTime":"2020-10-18T14:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T15:01:56.000Z","uid":200120,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46263c78bf48bee321267ab1e1acae33b35ff560","tid":2248433,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:50:18.000Z","msg":"就係青衣長發嘅鬍鬚仔同大埔嘅bulldog hot dog<br />\n<br />\n熱狗黎講就三大元素<br />\n<br />\n1.腸<br />\n2.配料<br />\n3.包皮<br />\n<br />\n先講腸，鬍鬚仔條腸大到仆街，俾班gay佬含都得，bulldog hot dog條腸就好有味，唔係齊柏林啲濕鳩珍寶腸咁。<br />\n<br />\n配料嚟講bulldog hotdog真係屈到仆街，我最鐘意德國風味，黑啤肉醬，仲有勁多口味揀。鬍鬚仔就得ret hot 肉醬正，不過勁撚好食。齊柏林就不過不失，叫正常普通。<br />\n<br />\n包皮兩間都烘過或者焗過，夠熱夠脆先好食，齊柏林舊包唔夠脆，差啲。<br />\n<br />\n兩間都50幾蚊一個餐包薯條飲品，性價比還可以。<br />\n<br />\n順便講埋薯條，鬍鬚仔就又長又粗嘅扁薯條，bulldog hotdog就係小食薯角咁，份量多，食埋個包好撚飽。<br />\n<br />\n雖則係咁踩齊柏林，不過齊柏林優勝位係薯條配千島醬，真係好正，唔會好似蕃茄醬食厭。<br />\n<br />\nPs 鬍鬚仔啲burger 都好高質，真係全能到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n鬍鬚仔條腸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iPywZEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiPywZEw.jpg&h=8ce3c795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df0bb2c3f54334ffe23d94011b8468f61f28b1a6","tid":2248433,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"On9 開錯台"},{"pid":"a8b2386b568f8ab9181c903abdf021d756975bc2","tid":2248433,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬍鬚仔<br />\n流撚哂口水 好想比條大腸後入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007ee45738de3758c53897b4a29a3af97e774849","tid":2248433,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"齊拍林呢？<br />\n雖然bull dog 真係好撚正"},{"pid":"ec6e042e0cf262fb431eae441bd859ce50ff34e3","tid":2248433,"uid":200120,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"007ee45738de3758c53897b4a29a3af97e774849","tid":2248433,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"齊拍林呢？<br />\n雖然bull dog 真係好撚正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:54:33.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，唔撚入流<br />\n<br />\n除咗多咗配料之外，根本同麵包鋪10蚊熱狗冇分別"},{"pid":"81694dac3bb87f6155adc40c0e1066669370fd76","tid":2248433,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:56:49.000Z","msg":"鬍鬚仔嗌餐我多數跟要餐湯唔要可樂<br />\n<br />\n個白湯夠濃夠香夠味<br />\n<br />\n同西餐廳個碗有得揮"},{"pid":"5833c68d39c20e731d2799f1e2e994c26ccefd02","tid":2248433,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"900d7402f029a6155a7a16e72334529d168ff1f4","tid":2248433,"uid":202256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5833c68d39c20e731d2799f1e2e994c26ccefd02","tid":2248433,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"黃圈 唔係好人經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}